    "attributes": {
        "action": "Amend employment law to require additional pay for Sunday working",
        "additional_details": "Many people would rather be elsewhere than working on a Sunday, as I think there\u2019s no incentive/benefit to working on a Sunday. I think there needs to be action for this to change to make employees want to work on a Sunday.",
        "background": "I\u2019d like the UK Government to mandate that anyone who works on a Sunday gets a pay increase of time and a half, since Sunday is an unsociable day to work.",
